data.Name: Matt Stell
data.Bio: “I dread answering the question ‘what kind of music do you play’ every time it’s asked.” Says Matt Stell & the Crashers’ front man Matt Stell. “Every time someone asks me, I just end up telling them that we’re kinda like 30 of my favorite bands and proceed to recommend songs and YouTube clips to them.” Matt Stell & the Crashers’ love for all kinds of music runs deep and they draw from many different sources for inspiration. Somewhere between Country Read more on Last.fm
